; : 161 2459 350 45 rc 0 0 0 sco F0_42
Ji 
161 2459 M 
-0.200 0 (         this.)A 
; : 161 2549 1650 45 rc 0 0 0 sco F0_42
Ji 
161 2549 M 
-0.200 0 (         Here are the two approaches that are under consideration:)A 
; : 161 2639 1900 45 rc 0 0 0 sco F0_42
Ji 
161 2639 M 
-0.200 0 (         1\) allow the template keyword in the template-name production, i.e.)A 
; : 161 2729 625 45 rc 0 0 0 sco F0_42
Ji 
161 2729 M 
-0.200 0 (            template-name)A 
; : 161 2774 1000 45 rc 0 0 0 sco F0_42
Ji 
